    "description": "<strong>Survive the Orcs</strong> is an Action fantasy Roguelike with RPG elements. Game breaking builds and hordes of enemies - each run is unique and full of slaughter! <br><br><strong>Upgrades, heroes, maps</strong> - how well can you mix them? Nuke groups of enemies, slowly burn them down or freeze them to death - your call. Explore the map for extra loot, build environmental sites that will aid you and find overpowered combos! Permanent enhancements is what you'll bring over to the next run.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight, explore &amp; loot</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202200/extras/fd1eb39b53376ec7f28af212302bf7e3.poster.avif?t=1686961246\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202200/extras/fd1eb39b53376ec7f28af212302bf7e3.webm?t=1686961246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202200/extras/fd1eb39b53376ec7f28af212302bf7e3.mp4?t=1686961246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Heroes, upgrades &amp; permanent enhancements</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202200/extras/8eea40fc16a6e7e3d0c5be67c6f83127.poster.avif?t=1686961246\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202200/extras/8eea40fc16a6e7e3d0c5be67c6f83127.webm?t=1686961246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202200/extras/8eea40fc16a6e7e3d0c5be67c6f83127.mp4?t=1686961246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Heroes </strong>- unique <strong>active spells</strong> and <strong>passive perks</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Endless upgrades</strong> - turn your hero into an overpowered monster. Each run is different!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Expand the environment</strong> - a couple of <strong><i>Flamethrowers </i></strong>in key locations should help</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Loot</strong> - reach it and it's yours</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Permanent enhancements</strong> - make your next runs easier</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Achievements.</strong> Can you collect them all?</li></ul><br><strong><i>Survive the Orcs</i></strong> is under development by a single indie developer - your support so far truly means a lot. Thank you and see you on the field slaying orcs!",
